      "en": "Median prices, the inventory squeeze, mortgage rates, and the LIRR commute math for South Shore Nassau and Suffolk in mid-2026 — with figures sourced from OneKey MLS, the Elliman/Miller Samuel report, Freddie Mac, the MTA, and FEMA.",
      "zh": "2026 年年中，长岛南岸 Nassau 与 Suffolk 县的房价中位数、库存紧张、房贷利率与 LIRR 通勤账——数据来自 OneKey MLS、Elliman/Miller Samuel 报告、房地美、MTA 与 FEMA。"
